cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.IR 

The paper discusses the use of deep learning approaches for glaucoma assessment from fundus photographs, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of a standardized benchmark strategy for evaluating different models, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses the clinical application of the proposed methods, which could fall under medical imaging (cs.MED) sub-category.
